Package common

Code shared between the client and server sides of the VPT
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Utils.NSAEFunction<T>
    An interface representing a function which throws a NoSuchAlgorithmException or NoSuchPaddingException
    Utils.TransformFunction<T>
    An interface representing a function which transforms its input
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Console
    Provides similar functionality to Console, allowing access to the system console or a desktop interface.
    Constants
    Constants shared by both the client and server side of the VPT
    DesktopConsole
    Provides similar functionality to Console but utilizing a desktop interface.
    Utils
    Provides utility functions
    Utils.IVCipher
    A class binding a Cipher to its iv
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Constants.Branch
    An enum representing the state of development of different sections of the VPT
